betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Need more bees to fuel your Beessentia factory? Beyond searching for hives and/or buying said hives/bees directly from the Coins, Coins, Coins tab, there is also the Swarmer if you've got access to Alvearies.

Swarmers are part of a quest in the How to Be(e) tab, so head over there for details.

You can also create more princesses using the Industrial Apicultural Acclimatiser and Drone Domestication Station, or just "Mega Apiary" as everyone actually calls it. Though note that multiblock is first craftable in UV.

The Mega Apiary also has a quest in the How to Be(e) tab.
